title: The 500 FPS Gaming PC!
description:
Today is the first day you can buy a 500Hz monitor! To celebrate, Linus is building a PC that can play games at 500 FPS… and will probably still bottom frag.

Play Enlisted for FREE on PC, Xbox Series X|S and PS®5: https://enplay.link/ltt. Follow the link to download the game and get your exclusive bonus now. See you in battle!
